<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-A"><h2>Highlights of the system</h2></div></p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Outfit rewards</p>

    <p>Along with the exericse hours accumulation, players can obtain the costumes and accessaries for the trainers. It can be treated like an award of your hard work.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Reminder of your persistence</p>

    <p>The game records the consecutive days of exercise, and allow players to put a stamp after daily training. This mechanism reminds your hard work of doing regular exercise.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Auto-calculation of Calorie and days of workouts</p>

    <p>Your hard work is represented by numbers. You can estimate how the game helps yourself burning Calorie along with the days.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Attractive Trainers</p>

    <p>For Japanese version, it hires <u>famous voice actors (JP)</u>, to guide players during the training. You can listen the guiding words with those voices. It is like to have a person doing exercise with you.</p>

    <p>You are able to <u>change the trainer</u>. You may choose a female or male trainer. They have a bit difference on their characteristics. Their words are quite encouraging.</p>

    <p>There are <u>an amount of clothes available for trainers</u>. You may change their clothing, while the options are opened.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Simple operation</p>

    <p>Once players select the trainning courses, the system will generate the courses with the chosen criteria every time. There needs no user intervention, and reduces the hestitation towards working out every day. If you want to change the training options, the time duration and trained body parts can be changed every time. If you are motivated to work out more than daily courses, or you want to focus more on dedicated body parts, the extra training courses are available.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p><br /><br /></p>
<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-B"><h2>Personal Experience</h2></div></p>

