<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Do not require much space and time for a training</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Change training plan easily</p>

    <ul>
      <li>It is able to change the training plan with personal needs.</li>
      <li>Workload is predictable and controllable</li>
      <li>It would not be too stressful to play for a long period.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Reasonable price</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Do not need to spend extra expenses for equipments.</li>
      <li>Longer play time means more worthiness.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>The training courses enhance the difficulties gradually</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Provide time for players to adapt the movement.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

<h3>Cons</h3>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>The exercise courses do not have much variation.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Players may get bored after playing for a period. I listen something else after an amount of gaming hours.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

